olive oil
1 packet Totara Tasty Cheddar
1 packet croissants
1 packet garlic aioli
1 packet Shaved Champagne Ham

Preheat oven to 220°C/200°C fan-forced. Thinly slice Totara Cheddar cheese. Cut croissants in half horizontally.

Spread croissant bases with garlic aioli and top with cheese and ham. Top with croissant tops and place on an oven tray. Bake until cheese is melted, 5-8 mins.

Divide croissants between plates.